## Phase 5: AI Leadership (Months 3-6)

### Next-Gen AI Features

#### 1. Scene Detection & B-Roll Suggestions
- Motion-based scene boundaries
- Auto-suggest B-roll from stock libraries
- Match visual style to existing content

#### 2. Auto-Captioning with Styling
- Animated captions (word-by-word highlight)
- Multiple caption styles (TikTok, YouTube, etc.)
- Automatic emoji insertion

#### 3. Content Repurposing Engine
- Turn 1-hour podcast into 10 shorts
- Extract highlights automatically
- Generate thumbnails from key frames

#### 4. Voice-to-Text Editing
- "Remove all instances of 'um'"
- "Cut everything before 'let's get started'"
- "Keep only the best takes"

